  <summary date="2019-05-09T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Promoting Reentry Through Education in Prisons Act of 2019 or the PREP Act

This bill establishes, within the Bureau of Prisons, an Office of Correctional Education. The office must provide educational services to incarcerated individuals in federal prisons and correctional institutions.</summary>
